sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Client
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant TASCtrl as TAS Controller<br/>Operator Pod
    participant LMESCtrl as LMES Controller<br/>Operator Pod
    participant GORCHCtrl as GORCH Controller<br/>Operator Pod
    participant EVALCtrl as EvalHub Controller<br/>Operator Pod
    participant TrustyAISvc as TrustyAI Service<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KServeISVC as KServe<br/>InferenceService
    participant LMEvalPod as LMEvalJob Pod<br/>18080/TCP HTTP
    participant Orchestrator as Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator<br/>8432/TCP HTTPS
    participant EvalHubSvc as EvalHub API<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant PostgreSQL as PostgreSQL<br/>TCP TLS
    participant MLFlow as MLFlow<br/>HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over User,KServeISVC: Flow 1: TrustyAI Model Monitoring Setup
        User->>K8sAPI: Create TrustyAIService CR<br/>Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>TASCtrl: Watch event
        TASCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment, Service, Route<br/>SA Token
        TASCtrl->>K8sAPI: Patch KServe InferenceService<br/>(add inference logger)
        KServeISVC->>TrustyAISvc: Inference logging data<br/>HTTPS/8443 TLS
        User->>TrustyAISvc: Query explainability/fairness<br/>via Route 443/TCP<br/>kube-rbac-proxy SAR
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
        Note over User,S3: Flow 2: LMEvalJob Execution
        User->>K8sAPI: Create LMEvalJob CR<br/>Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>LMESCtrl: Watch event
        LMESCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create evaluation Pod<br/>SA Token
        Note over LMEvalPod: Init: ta-lmes-driver copies<br/>binary to shared volume
        LMEvalPod->>HFHub: Download model/dataset (if online)<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
        LMEvalPod->>S3: Download offline models<br/>HTTPS/443 AWS IAM
        LMESCtrl->>LMEvalPod: Poll /GetStatus<br/>HTTP/18080 (pod exec)
        LMEvalPod-->>LMESCtrl: Progress (state, completion %)
        LMEvalPod->>S3: Upload results<br/>HTTPS/443 AWS IAM
        Note over LMESCtrl: Update LMEvalJob status
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over User,KServeISVC: Flow 3: Guardrails Orchestration
        User->>Orchestrator: POST request via Route<br/>HTTPS/443 reencrypt<br/>kube-rbac-proxy SAR
        GORCHCtrl->>K8sAPI: List InferenceServices<br/>(label: trustyai/guardrails=true)
        GORCHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Auto-generate orchestrator config
        Orchestrator->>KServeISVC: Generation request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS TLS (auto-detected)
        Orchestrator->>KServeISVC: Detector request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS TLS (auto-detected)
        Orchestrator-->>User: Guardrailed response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 255)
        Note over User,MLFlow: Flow 4: EvalHub Multi-Tenant Evaluation
        User->>EvalHubSvc: POST evaluation request<br/>via Route HTTPS/443<br/>kube-rbac-proxy SAR + X-Tenant
        EvalHubSvc->>PostgreSQL: Store evaluation data<br/>TCP TLS (optional)
        EvalHubSvc->>MLFlow: Track experiment<br/>HTTPS, projected SA Token (3600s TTL)
        EVALCtrl->>K8sAPI: Watch batch Jobs for failures
        Note over EVALCtrl: Detect OOMKilled,<br/>CrashLoopBackOff,<br/>ImagePullBackOff
        EVALCtrl->>EvalHubSvc: POST failure event<br/>HTTPS/8443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer SA Token
    end
